    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ユーリ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yuri</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>24</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>スタン</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Stahn</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ユーリ・ローウェル！
貴様には殺人の容疑がかかっている。
おとなしく僕達と共に来てもらおうか</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yuri Lowell! You are suspected of murder.
We'll need you to come with us quietly.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>こいつはヒューネガルドの騎士だな。
あっちの国にまで手配書が出回ってんのか</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>A knight from Hunegard, huh.
So there's a wanted poster of me
going around in that country too, huh.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>24</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>お偉いさん
よっぽどオレの事が憎いらしいな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Looks like those bigshots hate me a ton.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>24</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>なにを言ってるんだ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What're you talking about?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>こっちの話だ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It's no bussiness of yours.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>24</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>悪いが、捕まってやる気はないんでね。
突破させてもらうぜ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Sorry, but I'm not planning on getting caught.
I'll just have to break through you guys.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>24</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>一人で僕達に挑もうというのか</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Are you planning to challenge us by yourself?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>いいだろう！　受けて立つ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Very well. I accept your challenge.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
